  </p>

  <div class="sa-grid">
    <a href="/agentic-ai/sem-agentic" class="sa-card">
      <div class="sa-card-label">Agentische Systeme</div>
      <div class="sa-card-name">
        sem-agentic <span class="sa-card-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
